			<header class="comment-header">
				<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/1fe7cb53cb8354241ff02b72db5212c7?s=44&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' />				<cite class="comment-author">Jean</cite>
